        <header>Statutory Pay-As-You-Go Scorecards</header>
        <text display-inline="yes-display-inline">The budgetary effects of this Act shall not be entered on either PAYGO scorecard maintained pursuant to <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Statutory Pay-As-You-Go Act of 2010/s:4/ss:d">section 4(d) of the Statutory Pay-As-You-Go Act of 2010</cato:entity-ref>.</text>
