        <header>Senate PAYGO Scorecards</header>
        <text>The budgetary effects of this Act shall not be entered on any PAYGO scorecard maintained for purposes of <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="bill-by-number" value="110/sconres/21/s:201">section 201 of S. Con. Res. 21 (110th Congress)</cato:entity-ref>.</text>
